Staff Picks
Hi Wolf Iq,
One of the things I love love love about Woo is the control you have - especially compared to other platforms. It's also the theme of this month's email!
I've chosen a few products below that can help you level up while still doing things your way. After all, it's your store (and it always will be).
Colleen
Woo

PayHelm Reports & Analytics
A wise person once said, "If you can measure it, you can grow it." That's why PayHelm's customizable reporting tools are a powerful addition to your store.
Create sophisticated reports you can automate to uncover deeper insights about your business.
Take control of my data
Take control of my data

Name Your Price
Sometimes, it pays to be flexible. A great way to entice shoppers (and sell more) is by letting them pay what they want for an item.
With Name Your Price, you can suggest a minimum amount or leave it entirely in your customers' hands. It's also an excellent solution for collecting donations or selling gift cards.
Let buyers pay what they want
Let buyers pay what they want

Rental Products
Ecommerce isn't only about making sales. You can also use it to rent out items for recurring revenue!
Use this extension to customize every aspect of the rental process to suit your needs. From pricing and availability to deposits and add-ons, you have complete control from start to finish.
Rent out my products
Rent out my products

Conditional Fees

Add fixed or percentage charges

Set quantity limits

Run your store from anywhere
